Palm Gardens

An [unincorporated community](/Unincorporated_area) in [Clark County, Nevada](/Clark_County,_Nevada), United States.

Palm Gardens, a designation as vague as it is precise, marks an [unincorporated community](/Unincorporated_area) nestled within the expansive and often unforgiving landscape of [Nevada](/Nevada), specifically within [Clark County](/Clark_County,_Nevada), in the United States. It's one of those places that simply *is*, rather than having formally declared itself to be anything more.

